ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft4hl3cz7&h=728f6dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最正係鹽味連雞油滲曬落飯度<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2lc3m7h5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2lc3m7h5&h=bc3ed305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鹽腌得香、入味,無雪味<br />\n肉表面油潤,尚算嫩滑<br />\n質感有彈性<br />\n沙薑汁杰身,容易沾實雞用<br />\n令味道添層次<br />\n肝無臭味,入口唔會漿住漿住<br />\n唔好慳,貴d要肶最穩陣<br />\n<br />\n不過呢d細茶記仔有時水準會有偏差<br />\n今日嫩滑程度同雞味未算最高水準<br />\n可能同團年多人買雞有關<br />\n但八成功力已贏漢年、嘉華等名店"},{"pid":"84647c32de2283fca3a202578f6c52ccbce6c6ac","tid":89000,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7228e1fade0deed1da773c3d9d14f970a6dfaee5","tid":89000,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝收看"},{"pid":"dc6fe3ba0434b94800b17b454f42ced5906ebd60","tid":89000,"uid":8934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇上集link？"},{"pid":"4c9f81e153876ea77c5a437bb158d75d2138a7aa","tid":89000,"uid":7190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:34:44.000Z","msg":"睇錯一支九公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7778edbdb7f498c27f874cb7753e7fe28340f8ae","tid":89000,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想join....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀b今日都係一支公?"},{"pid":"34e9c1bb2a1a86e5c213ac0f3299636fc34e5665","tid":89000,"uid":62277,"li